choices.text:
what are the verb tenses?
1. Present Simple (for actions that happen regularly or habitually) 2. Present Continuous (for actions happening now, at this moment) 3. Past Simple (for completed actions in the past) 4. Past Continuous (for actions happening in the past, but not completed) 5. Future Simple (for actions that will happen regularly or habitually in the future) 6. Future Continuous (for actions happening in the future, at a specific time)
